      • passThrough

        public abstract def passThrough(context : SarlDocumentationParser.ParsingContext,
                                dynamicName : String,
                                parameter : String,
                                blockValue : String) : String 
        Description copied from class: SarlDocumentationParser.Tag
        Replies the string representation when this tag is interpreted.

        Usually, this function is called for obtaining the raw text, without the tags.

        Parameters:
        context - the parsing context.
        dynamicName - the name of the tag if it could be dynamically defined, or null.
        parameter - the value of tag parameter, or null if no parameter value.
        blockValue - the value inside the block, or null if not a block tag.
        Returns:
        the raw text for the tag.
